e=all\u0026amp;section=all\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eDebian package\u003c/a\u003e, courtesy of Stephen Kitt\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ea Ubuntu package is available from \u003ca href=\"http://packages.ubuntu.com/search?keywords=solaar\u0026amp;searchon=names\u0026amp;suite=all\u0026amp;section=all\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003euniverse repository\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ea \u003ca href=\"https://packages.gentoo.org/packages/app-misc/solaar\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eGentoo package\u003c/a\u003e, courtesy of Carlos Silva and Tim Harder\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ea \u003ca href=\"http://mageia.madb.org/package/show/release/cauldron/application/0/name/solaar\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eMageia package\u003c/a\u003e, courtesy of David Geiger\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/article\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
